# OptiEarth is the lightest and smoothest Fabric modpack ever.

All the best optimization mods put together and set for maximum performance.

## Offers:
- Extreme **FPS boost**;
- **Fast loading** for singleplayer worlds;
- More **advanced and faster** language menu;
- **Basilar** zoom mod;
- **In-game** fps counter and **much more!**

## FPS boost:
![FPS Boost:](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/4af44dee89772d98c0edd6bd4fc8a39833d81571.jpeg)
Tested on my own AMD RX 580 Series, AMD Ryzen 5 2600.
